Package be.ac.umons.jsonschematools.generator.exploration.handlers Description

Contains default implementations of handlers for the exploration generator. The produced values are abstracted. For instance, integer values are all represented by the special symbol \I. See AbstractConstants for all abstract values, and the non-API documentation for more information.
